              </p>

              <p style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.3; margin-top: 12px;">
                Following a structured SDLC offers several advantages:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li style="font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.3; margin-top: 12px;"><strong>Improved
                    Quality:</strong> Rigorous testing throughout the process minimises bugs and ensures a more reliable
